title: 이달의소녀탐구 #368 (LOONA TV #368)
summary:
The Second Day of Line&Up. OEC arrive in casual clothes.
0:18 -- OEC is ready for the day with the LipSoulRry Cross!
0:23 -- LOOΠΔ 1/3 arrive and are ready as well. HeeJin mentions this is the last day. "Fighting!"
